---
layout: base.njk
title: 文章归档
description: 所有文章按时间倒序排列。
permalink: /posts/index.html
---
<section class="archive-head">
  <p class="eyebrow">全部文章</p>
  <h1>文章归档</h1>
  <p>所有内容按时间倒序排列。以后只需要往 <code>src/posts/</code> 里放 Markdown 文件，网站就会自动更新。</p>
</section>

<section class="archive-list">
{% for post in collections.posts %}
  <a class="archive-item" href="{{ post.url }}">
    <time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
    <div>
      <h2>{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
      <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
    </div>
  </a>
{% endfor %}
</section>
